instructions.name: createTokenInfo
docs: create new token and initialize the virtual bonding pool of token <> wsol.

fields.name: launchpadBump
docs: used for generate seeds for signing on behalf the only Launchpad PDA account.

fields.name: minReserve
docs: min reserve on pool, this token will add into dex

fields.name: initialWsol
docs: The initial value of token (i.e. the initial wsol amount in virtual pool).

fields.name: createTokenFee
docs: fixed fee charged in wsol when create a new token.

fields.name: launchFee
docs: fixed fee charged in wsol when listing to a dex.

fields.name: tokenCount
docs: counter of tokens created in this protocol.

fields.name: virtualTokenAmount
docs: virtual bonding curve (Once 80% token was sold, the curve ends):

fields.name: accProtocolFee
docs: protocol fee has always been transfered to protocol token account,
here is only an accumulated counter

fields.name: accReferralFee
docs: referral fee  has always been transfered to referral token account,
here is only an accumulated counter

fields.name: accProxyFee
docs: proxy fee  has always been transfered to proxy token account,
here is only an accumulated counter

fields.name: accPrepaidFee
docs: prepaid fee  has always been transfered to protocol token account,
here is only an accumulated counter

fields.name: accVolume
docs: wsol amount involved in buy and sell, including fees

errors.name: NumberCastError
errors.msg: Unable to cast number into BigInt
